Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,↑Title↑
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.60,0:01:40.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遠野
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.90,0:01:46.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙從以前開始就容易招來災禍啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.00,0:02:06.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,近來如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.40,0:02:08.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在這裡做什麼啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.70,0:02:10.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大姊姊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.10,0:02:13.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呀呼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.60,0:02:15.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呀呼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.60,0:02:17.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次跟我約會喔
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.40,0:02:19.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呀呼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.70,0:02:22.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟我來一下
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.90,0:02:24.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  那傢伙搞什麼啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.00,0:02:26.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼就走了？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.10,0:02:29.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,志貴  等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.40,0:02:35.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  你怎麼了嘛？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.50,0:02:38.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底想做什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.50,0:02:41.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然隨便跑到學校來
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.70,0:02:43.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.90,0:02:45.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然不行
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.60,0:02:47.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你叫我怎麼跟大家解釋啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.30,0:02:50.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說實話不就好了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.60,0:02:52.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可能說得出口啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.70,0:02:55.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說什麼我們一起消滅吸血鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.40,0:03:12.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在懷疑我？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.10,0:03:15.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有辦法嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.60,0:03:17.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那種案件又發生了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.80,0:03:22.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是你想說Nero沒死？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.20,0:03:26.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來別人說的話你都沒在聽啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.40,0:03:29.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是說過我討厭血嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.60,0:03:32.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,何況Nero有吸血嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.30,0:03:35.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個嘛…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.90,0:03:45.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.10,0:03:48.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然這樣就說清楚啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.70,0:03:55.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  竟然懷疑到我身上
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.70,0:03:57.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  Nero是什麼人？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.00,0:04:03.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙不過是個刺客
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.10,0:04:05.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刺客？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.50,0:04:07.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他不是我要找的對象
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.10,0:04:08.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我希望志貴…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.90,0:04:09.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.40,0:04:14.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你希望我也幫忙找  對吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.00,0:04:17.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.90,0:04:19.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼時候開始？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.80,0:04:23.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就今晚九點在公園見
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.40,0:04:24.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.80,0:05:01.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您要出去嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.00,0:05:07.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是很重要的事情嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.00,0:05:13.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對志貴少爺來說是很重要的事情嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.20,0:05:28.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個請您拿去用
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.40,0:05:31.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是正門以及入口的鑰匙
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.50,0:05:35.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.30,0:05:39.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為志貴少爺是我的主人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.90,0:05:46.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你  翡翠小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.40,0:05:48.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫我翡翠就可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.50,0:05:52.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您不直接叫名字的話我會很不自在的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.70,0:05:57.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我出去了  翡翠
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.50,0:06:03.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,路上請小心  志貴少爺
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.80,0:06:39.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虛空之蛇？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.30,0:06:41.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有些人這麼稱呼Roa
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.40,0:06:43.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是個什麼樣的傢伙？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.90,0:06:47.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Roa為了追求永遠生命的極限
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.00,0:06:49.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放棄了對肉體的執著
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.70,0:06:50.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼意思？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.60,0:06:54.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙會轉生
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.40,0:06:55.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,轉生？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.10,0:06:59.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對Roa來說  肉體只不過是個容器
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.30,0:07:04.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在不斷更換容器之後
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.90,0:07:07.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他已經反覆轉生18次了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.30,0:07:10.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不是沒完沒了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.10,0:07:13.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.90,0:07:16.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在他轉生成什麼樣的人？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.00,0:07:18.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.80,0:07:19.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人在哪裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.50,0:07:24.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他發現我到了這個城市把氣息隱藏起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.20,0:07:27.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你打算怎麼找啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.70,0:07:30.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.40,0:07:37.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用你的眼睛看那傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.50,0:07:40.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.20,0:08:51.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,消  消失了？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.50,0:08:54.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是「死者」
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.60,0:08:55.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死者？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.50,0:08:58.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是被Roa吸過血的人類
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.40,0:09:01.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是Roa的手下啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.60,0:09:05.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些傢伙一面重複吸血行為一面增加自己的同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.90,0:09:07.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後把那些血供應Roa
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.50,0:09:11.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要繼續這樣獵殺死者
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.60,0:09:13.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙一定會有所行動
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.90,0:09:16.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想把他逼出來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.90,0:09:21.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.20,0:09:24.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你為什麼突然想幫忙了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.60,0:09:28.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前你不是非常不願意嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.00,0:09:32.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老實說到現在我還是不想牽扯進來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.60,0:09:34.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那為什麼要幫我？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.40,0:09:41.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概是因為痛苦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.90,0:09:46.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,痛苦？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.10,0:09:51.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以為弓塚被捲入事件當中的時候我覺得很痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.60,0:09:54.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.40,0:10:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為她是朋友又對我有種莫名的信賴
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.20,0:10:02.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就因為這樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.10,0:10:04.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.10,0:10:16.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說不定
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.60,0:10:21.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是志貴的話說不定能打倒Roa
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.40,0:10:22.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可能
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.70,0:10:24.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那可是連你都覺得難纏的對手啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.10,0:10:30.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你對自己的評價太低了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.70,0:10:55.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你對我的評價過高了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.70,0:11:23.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,睡眠不足嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.00,0:11:26.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有一點
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.40,0:11:28.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,熬夜不睡覺在做些什麼啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.70,0:11:30.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你胡扯什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.70,0:11:31.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.20,0:11:34.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有漂亮女朋友的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.10,0:11:37.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都說了  不是你想的那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.40,0:11:38.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.80,0:11:40.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也想要女朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.70,0:11:42.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都說了  她不是啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.80,0:11:55.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遠野
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.20,0:11:58.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學姊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.90,0:12:01.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不要喝杯茶？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.10,0:12:12.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請用
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.20,0:12:17.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真正規啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.40,0:12:23.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再怎麼說我也是茶道社的社長嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.60,0:12:26.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.90,0:12:31.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖說是社長  其實社員只有我一個人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.90,0:12:40.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝您的招待
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.90,0:12:42.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一杯粗茶不成敬意
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.40,0:12:44.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.60,0:12:48.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼突然請我喝茶？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.40,0:12:53.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遠野  你是不是有什麼煩惱？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.10,0:12:57.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近都沒什麼精神
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.60,0:13:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果方便說給我聽的話  可以找我談談喔
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.50,0:13:05.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是因為那個人嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.90,0:13:08.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個人是指？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.90,0:13:11.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天來學校的那個人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.10,0:13:31.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個人很危險
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.40,0:13:37.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是那種完全不考慮別人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.80,0:13:39.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既任性又自我中心
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.50,0:13:44.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到最後把人推下地獄的類型
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.50,0:13:46.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕對不會錯的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.60,0:13:51.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學姊你…認識她嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.10,0:13:55.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不認識
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.20,0:14:02.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.70,0:14:12.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的個性就是無法放著像遠野你這樣的人不管
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.00,0:14:47.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好慢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.20,0:14:48.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發生什麼事了？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.50,0:14:50.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為剛剛…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.90,0:14:53.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他只是邀請我而已
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.40,0:14:54.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說要跟我約會
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.00,0:14:58.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那叫作搭訕  對吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.60,0:15:01.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為突然跟我說話我還以為是敵人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.10,0:15:07.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的很危險啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.40,0:15:09.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你剛剛說了什麼嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.30,0:15:11.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.13,0:15:26.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好羨慕
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.80,0:15:36.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎…怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.30,0:15:39.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是Roa嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.70,0:15:42.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.70,0:15:48.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是說電動遊樂場嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.50,0:15:50.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,電動遊樂場？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.90,0:16:01.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  你要去哪裡啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.40,0:16:03.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們去玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.50,0:16:19.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到志貴這麼笨手笨腳
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.70,0:16:20.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.50,0:16:23.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那這裡是？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.30,0:16:29.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,電影院
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.80,0:16:32.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那接下來去這裡玩
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.70,0:16:33.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.60,0:16:36.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.80,0:16:40.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平常這個時間不會營業啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.40,0:16:44.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來是這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.83,0:16:45.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}(近期上映)
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.60,0:16:55.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過  一直做這種事真的沒關係嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.30,0:16:58.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目前都沒有發現任何氣息應該沒關係吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.50,0:17:04.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還是覺得很奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.00,0:17:05.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼很奇怪？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.80,0:17:09.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不但白天可以在外面走
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.60,0:17:10.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會吃飯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.10,0:17:14.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會去電動遊樂場玩  還要我帶你去電影院
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.50,0:17:17.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全不像啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.00,0:17:22.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,志貴被既有概念影響太深了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.60,0:17:29.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我以前不巧沒有當吸血鬼的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.50,0:17:33.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我們差不多該走了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.20,0:17:35.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天算我請你的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.50,0:17:37.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦！ 這樣好嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.00,0:17:38.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要逞強喔
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.30,0:17:40.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒問題的  交給我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.70,0:17:43.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多謝招待
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.80,0:17:45.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我們再去喝一杯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.80,0:17:46.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好主意
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.80,0:17:51.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.90,0:17:55.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我請你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.00,0:17:59.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勝利者必須要同情戰敗者才對
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.70,0:18:05.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩位總共是2352圓
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.80,0:18:07.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍等一下喔
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.20,0:18:14.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝光臨
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.60,0:18:17.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,志貴  等一下啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.80,0:18:18.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要管  快點走
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.50,0:18:31.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你剛剛做的事情可是犯罪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.20,0:18:34.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是不夠用所以複製一下而已啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.70,0:18:37.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是犯罪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.70,0:18:41.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽好  你就算不做這種事就已經夠引人注目了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.10,0:18:44.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你是說這都是我的錯？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.20,0:18:46.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是這個意思
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.90,0:18:48.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過  要找Roa的話
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.70,0:18:50.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在不要太引人注目不是比較好嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.80,0:18:54.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真拿你沒辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.80,0:18:57.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然我不是很認同  但是志貴這樣說的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.00,0:19:01.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你那邊怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.80,0:19:05.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概是在哪個地方割到了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.70,0:19:07.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為走得很匆忙
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.50,0:19:45.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.20,0:19:49.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是什麼嚴重的傷
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.80,0:19:51.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.20,0:19:54.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天就到此為止
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.40,0:20:03.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.70,0:20:32.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好久不見了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.50,0:20:36.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Arcueid Brunestud
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.20,0:20:41.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ciel  你又想被我殺死嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.20,0:20:45.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被遠野殺死時的傷還沒完全好的你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.80,0:20:47.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有辦法做得到嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.70,0:20:50.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找我到底有什麼事？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.60,0:20:52.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你現在的目的應該跟我一樣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.30,0:20:54.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.80,0:20:56.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就給我退下
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.80,0:20:57.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太礙眼了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.30,0:20:59.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那可不行
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.30,0:21:03.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不能看著遠野遇到危險
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.80,0:21:05.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很可惜
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.30,0:21:07.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這件事志貴已經同意了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.50,0:21:11.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對他來說最危險的是你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.20,0:21:18.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對你這八百年來的自我壓抑我表示敬意
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.70,0:21:22.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過  那也到達極限了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.70,0:21:23.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這是什麼意思
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.90,0:21:28.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有人可以反抗本能的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.50,0:21:34.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛剛那是警告
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.80,0:21:36.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果遠野出了什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.80,0:21:39.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定會解決掉你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.30,0:21:42.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我等著
